info.headline: Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued September 05 at 6:49PM CDT until September 05 at 11:00PM CDT by NWS Duluth
info.description: SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 669 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 11 PM CDT THIS EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS IN MINNESOTA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 6 COUNTIES IN EAST CENTRAL MINNESOTA AITKIN PINE IN NORTHEAST MINNESOTA CARLTON COOK LAKE ST. LOUIS IN WISCONSIN THIS WATCH INCLUDES 7 COUNTIES IN NORTHWEST WISCONSIN ASHLAND BAYFIELD BURNETT DOUGLAS IRON SAWYER WASHBURN THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF AITKIN, ASHLAND, BAYFIELD, CASTLE DANGER, CLOQUET, DULUTH, GRAND MARAIS, GRANTSBURG, HAYWARD, HINCKLEY, HURLEY, PINE CITY, SHELL LAKE, SILVER BAY, SPOONER, SUPERIOR, TWO HARBORS, AND WASHBURN. THIS ALSO INCLUDES THE TRIBAL LANDS OF THE FOND DU LAC BAND, BROOKSTON DISTRICT, THE ST. CROIX BAND IN BURNETT COUNTY, THE RED CLIFF BAND, THE GRAND PORTAGE RESERVATION, THE FOND DU LAC BAND, CLOQUET DISTRICT, THE BAD RIVER RESERVATION, THE NORTHWESTERN AREA OF THE LAC DU FLAMBEAU BAND, THE LAC COURTE OREILLES RESERVATION, THE FOND DU LAC BAND, SAWYER DISTRICT, THE MILLE LACS BAND, LENA LAKE, EAST LAKE, BIG SANDY LAKE AND, HINCKLEY AREAS AND THE BOIS FORTE BAND, LAKE VERMILION AND, NETT LAKE AREAS.
